trans-unit.source: The DsmlSoapHttpConnection class represents a connection to a DSML Gateway using SOAP over HTTP.
trans-unit.target: Klassen DsmlSoapHttpConnection representerer en tilkobling til en DSML gatewayen ved hjelp av SOAP sikkerhetskoder.

trans-unit.source: The method will block while waiting for a response from the DSML server and will time out according to the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryConnection.Timeout%2A> property.

trans-unit.source: Thrown when a session is already open on the connection.
trans-unit.target: Et når en økt som er allerede åpen for tilkoblingen.

trans-unit.source: Thrown when the XML returned from the Server in response to the BeginSession is not well-formed.
trans-unit.target: Et når XML ble returnert fra serveren som svar på BeginSession ikke er riktig formet.

trans-unit.source: Thrown when there is a communications failure with the DSML server or when the server is out of available sessions.
trans-unit.target: Et når det er en kommunikasjonsfeil med DSML-server, eller når serveren er ikke nok tilgjengelig økter.

trans-unit.source: The EndSession method ends the session with the DSML server and clears the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.SessionId*> property.
trans-unit.target: Metoden EndSession avslutter økten med DSML-serveren, og fjerner den <xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.SessionId*>egenskapen.</xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.SessionId*>

trans-unit.source: The method will block while waiting for a response from the DSML server and will time out according to the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryConnection.Timeout%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Metoden vil blokkere under venting på et svar fra serveren DSML og blir tidsavbrutt i henhold til den <xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryConnection.Timeout%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryConnection.Timeout%2A>

trans-unit.source: If the DSML server has already terminated the session on its own, a <xref:System.Net.WebException> will be thrown.
trans-unit.target: Hvis DSML serveren har allerede avsluttet økten på sin egen, en <xref:System.Net.WebException>vil bli utløst.</xref:System.Net.WebException>

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.SessionId%2A> is still valid after the exception is thrown, the request never reached the server and the connection is still considered valid.
trans-unit.target: Hvis den <xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.SessionId%2A>er fortsatt er gyldige når den unntak, forespørselen nådde aldri serveren, og tilkoblingen er fortsatt gyldig.</xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.SessionId%2A>
